  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[because of not being around just adults all the time.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[In my experience, being an only child you are more serious.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[On the negative, a larger family costs a whole lot more.]]></edu>
